  <title>Region</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Region</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3">Wirkbereich</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">GVL_&lt;Sequence1&gt;_Driver</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3">Syntax</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">{region &quot;GVL: Input&quot;}, {region &quot;GVL: Output&quot;}</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3">Beschreibung</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Normal">In Kombination mit dem Attribut HARDWARE(true) erfolgt eine Deklaration als</text><text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"> </text><text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:italic; text-decoration:none; color:#339966;">&quot;GVL: Input&quot;</text><text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"> </text><text styleclass="Normal">oder</text><text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"> </text><text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:italic; text-decoration:none; color:#339966;">&quot;GVL: Output&quot;</text><text styleclass="Normal">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Beispiel:<text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"> </text><text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#3366ff;">AT</text><text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"> %I*</text>,<text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"> </text><text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#3366ff;">AT</text><text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"> %Q*</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Achtung">Hinweis: Dies gilt nur bei Beckhoff-Systeme </para>
